<hometopic>Style Manager Help

                        <!-- **** UNRESOLVED IDs **** -->
                        <location id=VUEUsingHelp><\location>

With Style Manager, you can easily customize the visual elements and
system behavior of the desktop.  Choose or modify the color palette,
select a font, change the behavior of your mouse, or perform other tasks
that tailor the desktop environment to suit your preferences.

